ote><br />\n巴打車長？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十幾年前親眼睇住個司機朋友係黃竹坑對開咁做同另一個行家係度玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時至今日輪到我都唔會玩呢啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到依家咪又係玩公路落斜 N 波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然唔係部部車可以因為依家啲車要踩迫力入波<br />\n要搵部踩少少就入到既車玩"},{"pid":"57613bf82aff0c803d647e06090adbfc99cf1676","tid":106071,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇真係轉到既睇？</blockquote><br />\n佢有轉到 但係個電腦唔俾佢轉 可能為左保護架車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n渣緊歐洲車，轉唔到同響alarm 之外，根本無嘢會發生"},{"pid":"9c794aaad7718387b0813b17397093345d8ea32f","tid":106071,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T07:04:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵架棍波車試下</blockquote><br />\n入唔到呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得幾km/h咁入都掃波牙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好牙我老母</blockquote>支波棍啪斷都唔會推得入<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}